TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
sorry sir, we did not mean for that

waiter! Jeb has an armada in my soup!

Send the Spanish Armada there immediately!

Waiter there is a trumpet in my soup!

Here, let me blow it out for you!

Waiter, there's Yogurt is in my soup! (Spaceballs reference)

I'm sorry sir, but you ordered yogurt soup!

Waiter! Jeb is planting a nuclear device in my soup!

Don't worry, we've taken out the plutonium.

Waiter, there's a singularity in my soup!

Better gobble it up before it gobbles YOU up! O_O

Waiter, there's Sampa Claus in my soup.

that is me sir.

waiter why am I in a soup?

Because you taste awesome.

Waiter, there's a space shuttle in my soup.

Oh well. It is for the greater good of the people who are still alive... still alive. Please do not kill me.

Waiter, there is a cat in my soup.

Is there a problem with that?

Waiter, the soup just said my name.

That's because it has a talking fish in it!

Waiter, there's a waiter in my soup!

That's part of the "Waiter's Special" dish.

Waiter, there's an entire star system in my soup?

Those are meatballs.

Waiter, there's a goblin in my soup!

You must be seeing things I don't see a goblin...

you must be playing too much Dota 2

Waiter there is a kerbal in mah soup!

Oh goodness we're doomed!

Waiter there is an M4 Sherman (WWII Tank) in my soup!

Counter it with a Panzer!

Waiter there is a wormhole in me soup!

Close the iris, there might be jaffa on the other side.

waiter there is soup in my soup!

Then eat it up before it gets cold!

Waiter, there's a girl in my soup! (sorry, running out of ideas)

you asked for a soupy girl.

Waiter, theres a Nuke and a Creeper in my soup!
